Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.24,0:00:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sirius: Sirius! Yeah! Yes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.18,0:00:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Ah... looks like they got a\NTaylor Lautner poster in here too...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.54,0:00:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they are everywhere...\Nin every single room...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.97,0:00:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you kids doing here?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.49,0:00:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We've come to break you free!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.83,0:00:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! But Umbridge is coming with\Na whole army of dementors and...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.49,0:00:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...and they're gonna kiss you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.06,0:00:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand back! Alohomora!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.19,0:00:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, magic!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.83,0:00:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sirius!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.05,0:00:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you're seen being helping me\Nyou'll all be in really big trouble!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.14,0:00:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't... we don't care! You're innocent!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.14,0:00:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but who's gonna believe a bunch of kids...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.51,0:00:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...and a no-good washed up loser like Malboy?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.16,0:00:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And me, the most wanted criminal in the world, I mean...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.16,0:00:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...god, what kind of a dumbass will believe this bunch?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.73,0:00:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This dumb... --This dumbass!\N[troubles with opening the door ;-)]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.84,0:00:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Lupin!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.43,0:00:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Lupin, Sirius is innocent!\NIf you just let me explain...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.96,0:01:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry, there is no need to explain.\NI know that he's innocent and I've got proof!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.39,0:01:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT?!? How?!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.68,0:01:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This! The Maraunders Map!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.68,0:01:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on the Hogwartsexpress when I began\Nto get chilly and I decided to use it as a blanket.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.50,0:01:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when I noticed a name on there\Nthat shouldn't have been there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.66,0:01:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The name of a man that I believed to be long dead.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.18,0:01:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Peter Pettigrew!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.56,0:01:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That rat-bastard!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.54,0:01:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.65,0:01:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry, Long ago your father was friends\Nwith Sirius and best friends with me, but...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.06,0:01:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...he had -- another friend.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.15,0:01:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It's impossible. You can't\Nhave more then two friends!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.70,0:01:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a fatal mistake.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.70,0:01:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Peter Pettigrew betrayed your parents\Nand killed all those people!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.69,0:01:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- Then he set me up and disappeared!\N- Until now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.51,0:01:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cuz he's in this room!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.78,0:01:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!? Where...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.22,0:01:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.78,0:01:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...there!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.97,0:01:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.15,0:01:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron, how could you? You traitor!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.85,0:01:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill him, chaps! And then she'll be all mine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.85,0:01:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.71,0:02:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I... something's wrong, I'm not Peter Pettigrew!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.03,0:02:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The map's never wrong, Ron.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.05,0:02:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should I say Peter?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.62,0:02:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No, wait! Wait! If you look at the map,\NPeter Pettigrew's name is on top of Ron's!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.87,0:02:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That must mean that\NPeter Pettigrew -- is on top of Ron!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.89,0:02:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Scabbers!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.48,0:02:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have magiced himself into a rat!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.66,0:02:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That totally makes sense!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.91,0:02:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.98,0:02:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stomp him!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.14,0:02:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he put up a fight, but he is dead now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.88,0:02:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The nightmare is over!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.13,0:02:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's... weird.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.93,0:02:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The map says Peter Pettigrew hasn't moved,\Nbut... it must be wrong...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.45,0:02:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the map is never wrong.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.84,0:02:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Whahahahahaha!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.31,0:02:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... it's... it's...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.61,0:02:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Peter Pettigrew!!! Aaaaaaaah!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.04,0:02:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally figured it out.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.13,0:02:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Expelliarmus!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.76,0:03:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna drug and kill you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.76,0:03:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you betray\NJames and Lilly like that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.81,0:03:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. James was my best friend.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.17,0:03:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was his best friend...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.22,0:03:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Dark Lord, he can be very persuasive.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.40,0:03:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He offered me a robot hand.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.40,0:03:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And all I got was this lousy T-shirt.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.85,0:03:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're never gonna get away with this. Now that we found you,\NSirius is gonna be free and you're gonna go to Azkaban!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.28,0:03:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I've got a better idea.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.26,0:03:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How about I'll kill all of you\Nand get away scot-free...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.01,0:03:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... ahm, really... no, no!\NYou should go to jail.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.\N- We could vote on it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.94,0:03:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Vote? Why don't you VOTE on\Nwhat's gonna be on your tombstone?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.48,0:03:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Red vines!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.52,0:03:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Red vines!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.93,0:03:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Poster-man!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.57,0:03:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't killing us taste better with a red vine?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.73,0:03:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,'Course!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.48,0:03:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything tastes better with red vines!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.66,0:04:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you have one?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.29,0:04:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Weasley.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.40,0:04:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna trust you this time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.31,0:04:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to see any funny tricks!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No tricks, just treats...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.88,0:04:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want you to hold out that delicious...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.22,0:04:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...red stick of candy...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.04,0:04:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be right here...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.97,0:04:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- ... and I want you to... just stay right there\Nso I can put my mouth around it.\N- It's gonna be right here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.88,0:04:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, here I go!\NYummy yummy yummy...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.53,0:04:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupefy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.83,0:04:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Red vines: What the hell can't they do?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it, Ron!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.26,0:04:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! That was....Great!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.28,0:04:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your poster-boy days are over, Peter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.80,0:04:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to jail. Crucio!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.76,0:04:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Ron, we're sorry about your rat.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.51,0:04:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Sorry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.98,0:04:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.50,0:05:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been dead for years.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.03,0:05:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sirius, ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.77,0:05:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm sorry that I doubted you for all those years.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.80,0:05:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you think I would betray\NJames and Lilly like that, I mean, I was his best friend!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.93,0:05:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell am I?!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought you were his best friend?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.48,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.52,0:05:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell you what.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.27,0:05:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one way to settle this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.16,0:05:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,From this moment on...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.31,0:05:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...YOU and ME will be the best friends!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.99,0:05:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I ever wanted...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.35,0:05:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Touch down!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.00,0:05:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, Lupy!
